00:02:21.489 --> 00:02:24.569
&gt;&gt;Joel: Thank you.

00:02:24.569 --> 00:02:26.579
Are these yours?

00:02:26.579 --> 00:02:28.930
[chuckles] I need them but they're not mine.

00:02:28.930 --> 00:02:29.930
All right.

00:02:29.930 --> 00:02:33.689
Well, it is a real distinct honor to be here
