00:31:03.750 --> 00:31:05.450
project for compost.

00:31:05.450 --> 00:31:09.640
You'll get this wonderful epiphany that you
understand some of the wonderful things you've

00:31:09.640 --> 00:31:16.340
heard about elitism and we can't feed the
world will be set in their cultural context

00:31:16.340 --> 00:31:19.630
as we carry the past into the future.

00:31:19.630 --> 00:31:25.850
Because my belief is that the chances are
the next hundred years we will need to return

00:31:25.850 --> 00:31:37.110
to a more localized, truly solar driven, carbon
cycling, biomimicked, kind of existence than

00:31:37.110 --> 00:31:43.649
we have learned to enjoy in the last 50 years
as we have abdicated historical normalcy in

00:31:43.649 --> 00:31:45.620
our civilization.

